NAME
	assist

SYNOPSYS
	assist
	assist <name>

DESCRIPTION
	When a friend of yours is in combat and you want to help him, the
	assist command lets you join your friend in combat with the third
	party without having to figure out the exact description if the
	assailant.

	To kill another (interactive) player, add an exclamation mark at the
	end of the command to indicate your determination.

OPTIONS
	[none]	If you are in a team, assist a member of the team.
	<name>	The name or description of the living you want to assist
		in combat. Note that you will help <name> and attack the
		enemy of <name>.

SEE ALSO
	kill
